
Generate fonts using something like:

For TeXLive:

  mktexpk --mfmode ibmvga --mag 1 --bdpi 110 --dpi 110 cmr10
  --> /var/tmp/fonts/pk/ibmvga/public/cm/cmr10.110pk

for teTeX:

  MakeTeXPK cmr10 110 110 1 ibmvga
  --> /var/lib/texmf/fonts/pk/ibmvga/public/cm/cmr10.110pk
  MakeTeXPK cmr10 220 110 2 ibmvga
  --> /var/lib/texmf/fonts/pk/ibmvga/public/cm/cmr10.220pk

use `kpsewhich pk cmr10.110pk' to find the file.
